name: ɪᴛ'ꜱ ᴀʟʟ ᴀʙᴏᴜᴛ ᴍᴇᴍᴏʀɪᴇꜱ
description:
To stop and think. 

to withdraw, to fold, to fold and to fold back 

memories, ideas.

To tone down, to slow down the pace. 

To escape the monotony of permanent novelty, of distractions constantly administered. 

Think about what we are abandoning.
_____________________________________________________________

Detenerse a pensar. 

Replegarse, plegar y replegar 

recuerdos, ideas. 

Bajar el tono, bajar el ritmo. 

Escapar a la monotonía de la novedad permanente, de las distracciones administradas en forma constante. 

Pensar en lo que estamos abandonando. 


𝘷𝘪𝘥𝘦𝘰 𝘢𝘯𝘥 𝘱𝘩𝘰𝘵𝘰𝘨𝘳𝘢𝘱𝘩𝘺 𝘸𝘪𝘵𝘩 𝘥𝘪𝘨𝘪𝘵𝘢𝘭 𝘦𝘥𝘪𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘨
